sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant Claude as "Claude Code"
    participant HookSys as "Hook System"
    participant SyncHook as "sync-guides.mjs"
    participant Command as "/arckit.pages Command"
    participant FS as "File System"
    
    User->>Claude: /arckit.pages
    Claude->>HookSys: Trigger UserPromptSubmit
    HookSys->>SyncHook: Execute sync-guides hook
    
    Note over SyncHook: Step 1: Sync Guides
    SyncHook->>FS: walkMdFiles(sourceDir)
    SyncHook->>FS: Copy plugin/docs/guides/*.md<br/>to repo docs/guides/
    SyncHook->>SyncHook: extractTitle() for each guide
    
    Note over SyncHook: Step 2: Repository Info
    SyncHook->>FS: Read .git/config
    SyncHook->>SyncHook: parseRepoInfo()<br/>Extract owner, repo, branch
    SyncHook->>FS: Read plugin VERSION file
    
    Note over SyncHook: Step 3: Template Processing
    SyncHook->>FS: Read pages-template.html
    SyncHook->>SyncHook: Replace {{OWNER}}, {{REPO}},<br/>{{BRANCH}}, {{VERSION}}
    SyncHook->>FS: Write docs/index.html
    
    Note over SyncHook: Step 4: Project Scanning
    SyncHook->>FS: listDir(projects/)
    SyncHook->>SyncHook: scanGlobalDocs()
    SyncHook->>SyncHook: scanProject() for each
    SyncHook->>SyncHook: buildManifest()
    SyncHook->>FS: Write docs/manifest.json
    
    Note over SyncHook: Step 5: Stats Computation
    SyncHook->>SyncHook: Count guides, projects,<br/>documents, diagrams, etc.
    SyncHook-->>HookSys: Return additionalContext<br/>with stats
    
    HookSys-->>Command: Inject stats in prompt
    Command->>Command: Format summary<br/>using hook stats only
    Command-->>User: Display summary<br/>(NO tool calls)
